{"tid":2065081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：倫敦白左暴徒下個拆毀目標 ：大英博物館","createTime":"2020-06-15T09:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T12:37:44.000Z","uid":1241,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"506e31bb41d969123b5cdc31604f94ce33fd0b40","tid":2065081,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"倫敦黑白暴左下一搶掠拆毀目標：大英博物館。<br />\n<br />\n因為館內大量藏品，據說是「帝國主義者」由非洲和遠東之清國搶來。因此多年來，大英博物館內許多中國遊客，在明清瓷器舘內，見大量藏品，俱咬牙切齒，十分憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n對此香港人一直戀殖而旁觀，毫無感覺，或思想落後，覺得此等珍寶永久藏在大英博物館是「利大於弊」，而且許多人在等BNO，不敢造次。在英國留學的一些遠東愛國战狼，又未知會Stand by 會師否？<br />\n<br />\n英國警察又軟弱無能，一舉洗雪國恥，實在充滿誘惑。<br />\n<br />\n不過，身為歷史的旁觀者，希望這等黑人左膠，化解情緒、壓抑對白人的種族仇恨，切勿做蠢事呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3906264722779355/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F3906264722779355%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7g8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=df9ad98a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3906264722779355/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8541a6e9b9a71e70283d9e7d1ca2cf0c73439ccd","tid":2065081,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"左癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d8e527ea8f2acc7579e422468269de189787e9","tid":2065081,"uid":58164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b452f7116490d2bd99dadd4013b0ef8dc14f36d9","tid":2065081,"uid":161935,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"啱哂比伊斯蘭國統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803b1178f18a721592fbce553c44eb4a19e79eb7","tid":2065081,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-1